'''''Bulletin of the Modern Humanities Research Association'' 20''' is an issue (number 20, October [[1923]]) of the ''Bulletin of the Modern Humanities Research Association''. It includes an obituary by [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] for [[Henry Bradley]], entitled ''[[Henry Bradley, 3 Dec., 1845-23 May, 1923]]'' (pp. 4â€“5).

A copy seen was bound with other issues into a single volume.
